WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.800 --> 00:00:13.810
So far we've been writing and
running functions.

2
00:00:13.810 --> 00:00:18.600
Now we want to start writing and
running whole programs.

3
00:00:18.600 --> 00:00:24.320
And on a Macintosh and on Linux machines,
Python 2 comes installed.

4
00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:28.794
Your machine may attempt to
run our programs in Python 2,

5
00:00:28.794 --> 00:00:32.915
which doesn't work, or
it may run them in Python 3.

6
00:00:32.915 --> 00:00:36.430
We're going to determine that right now.

7
00:00:36.430 --> 00:00:44.270
Go up to spotlight, type in terminal,
press enter, run it.

8
00:00:44.270 --> 00:00:47.180
Type Python, press return.

9
00:00:49.120 --> 00:00:53.847
On my machine it returns
Python 3 point something, so

10
00:00:53.847 --> 00:00:59.007
mine is going to run Python 3
automatically, yours may too.

11
00:00:59.007 --> 00:01:03.066
If it does, skip to the next video, you
don't need to create an environment for

12
00:01:03.066 --> 00:01:03.680
Python 3.

13
00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:07.700
If yours displays Python 2 point
something, then you need to

14
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:11.520
create an environment, and I'm going to
show you how to do that very quick.

15
00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:13.540
Okay, let me exit from Python.

16
00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:19.688
First, let me show you how to determine
what version of Python you're using.

17
00:01:23.218 --> 00:01:27.926
Okay, if I bring Spyder up,
mine says 3.6.2,

18
00:01:27.926 --> 00:01:32.280
you should do that and
write down the version.

19
00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:34.903
If you installed an environment for
that version,

20
00:01:34.903 --> 00:01:38.014
I think it will go a little bit
faster than if you install it for

21
00:01:38.014 --> 00:01:41.187
a different version,
although it'll work perfectly fine.

22
00:01:41.187 --> 00:01:46.030
Once you've done that, Go back to this.

23
00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:50.713
Now I will show you how to determine if
you have an environments already on your

24
00:01:50.713 --> 00:01:51.370
machine.

25
